  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Arrival of fuel ships further delayed: Do not wait in queues - Kanchana Wijesekera",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Although it was earlier reported that two petrol and diesel ships would arrive in the country last Thursday and Friday, their arrival will be further delayed, Power Minister Kanjana Wijesekera said.",
        "He also apologized for the earlier announcement made by him regarding the arrival of the ships in question.",
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) has been informed by the importers that petrol and diesel ships arriving in the country last Thursday and Friday will arrive a day late. I also made that announcement last Thursday.",
        "However, it was later announced that the ships would be further delayed in arriving in the country.",
        "I therefore apologize for the earlier notice regarding the fuel ship. New arrival dates for ships will be announced later.",
        "Meanwhile, Minister Kanjana Wijesekera said that 84 petrol stations have been set up to supply fuel to health services.",
        "These are supplied with 6600 liters of petrol and diesel each. The amount of fuel that can be supplied to the health service has been notified to the relevant parties through the Petroleum Corporation. ' As mentioned.",
        "It was expected that the fuel crisis would be partially resolved after the aforementioned fuel ships arrived in the country last week.",
        "Despite this, it has been reported that the arrival date of the ships cannot be announced at present, which has caused dissatisfaction among the people.",
        "It is noteworthy that people who have been waiting in line to get fuel for a long time but have not been able to get it, continue to block the streets and engage in protests."
      ],
